    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in mint condition, and prospective buyers will find it to be an exceptional, like-new option that is rarely seen on the used market. The exterior is flawless, with no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections \u2014 it presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally impressive, featuring pristine upholstery, spotless carpeting, and all controls and features functioning perfectly with no signs of wear. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with all mechanical systems in top working order and full service history available. The tires have excellent tread depth, the brakes are in excellent condition, and all electronics \u2014 including infotainment, climate control, and safety systems \u2014 operate flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that truly feels new, ideal for a buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Honest Budget Buy \u2014 A Fixer-Upper With Potential! \u2014 If you're a hands-on buyer or a DIY mechanic looking for an affordable project, take a look at this one! We'll be completely upfront: this vehicle is in poor condition and will need some meaningful work to get it road-ready \u2014 but that's exactly reflected in the price! Great for someone with the skills and vision to bring it back to life. Come take a look and see if it's the right project for you!",
      "price": 5750.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Honest Deal on a Project Car \u2014 Priced to Move! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in poor condition, and we're keeping it real with you! It has noticeable wear inside and out, along with mechanical issues that will need attention. That said, it could be a great opportunity for a handy DIYer, a parts source, or someone looking for a budget restoration project! We've priced it fairly to reflect its current state \u2014 no surprises, just straightforward value. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for your next project! \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we are committed to full honesty with every potential buyer. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple dents, deep scratches, faded or peeling paint, and possibly some rust or corrosion in areas. The interior has seen better days, with worn or torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car requires attention \u2014 there are known issues that will need repair before reliable daily use, and a thorough inspection by a qualified mechanic is strongly recommended before purchase. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer looking for a project car, a parts source, or someone prepared to invest in substantial repairs. It is priced accordingly to reflect its current state, and there are no hidden surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're happy to present a reliable, well-maintained example that offers genuine value. The exterior presents nicely \u2014 you'll notice only minor cosmetic wear such as a few light surface scratches and perhaps a small scuff or two, but nothing that detracts meaningfully from its overall appearance. The paint retains good depth and shine. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing normal use but no significant damage \u2014 seating surfaces, trim, and controls are all in solid working order. Mechanically, this car runs well and has been properly maintained; you can expect a dependable driving experience. This is a solid, honest vehicle that represents a practical and worthwhile purchase for the right buyer.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    }
